{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 13:00:53.163813", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary\n- Is anomaly: true\n- Faulty devices: switch_1\n- Root cause: p4_table_entry_misconfig\n\nRationale\n- End-to-end connectivity fails in both directions.\n- switch_1 receives packets on both interfaces but transmits none, blackholing traffic.\n- switch_2 forwards correctly and shows valid LPM hits.\n- switch_1 shows control-plane inconsistency (Thrift CLI inaccessible) and no runtime pipeline logs, indicating its forwarding table state is incorrect or not applied, consistent with a P4 table entry misconfiguration.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1770, "output_tokens": 120, "total_tokens": 1890, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
